  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Improve Reading Culture among 500 Kids in Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will foster the love of reading among 500 vulnerable kids in 20 deprived villages in Nigeria.   The targeted kids lack interest in reading due to lack of books and poor motivation.  Twenty volunteers, one from each of the 20 village will be recruited and trained, so that each will have reading sessions with 25 children twice a week for 1 year.  At the end of the year, a &quot;Reading Fiesta&quot; will be held where each child will be awarded 5 books to take home and read with their families.</narrative>
  </description>
